{
  "stem": "1895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 56.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I don't know that I ever saw anything more cruel than that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The people had been broken in the first place, because at the time, most of the hangings were for escape attempts.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a lot of the hangings that I watched were for people who were involved in the uprising that I described.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After the uprising, they caught a lot of the sonderkommando that had escaped, that they made it out of the camp, and then they caught them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They caught most of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sonderkommando, which are the people that worked in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the ones who started--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were the ones who started the uprising.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was September-- the beginning of September '44, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was a period where I lived in a haze.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fortunately, because of the fact that I worked near the ramp, I was not hungry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was able to get food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the people who kept coming in brought a lot of food with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of that food made its way back outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the usual comment was-- the Polish boys who worked with us, the Russian boys who worked with us on that kommando, they would usually comment if-- if-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] if a trainload arrived from Hungary, they would say tomorrow we eat Hungarian salami.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the world.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
